    {
      "chinese": "原住民重視祖靈信仰，相信祖靈居住在山上，並且會保護族人收穫豐盛，而且各族都有自己獨特的祭典，例如: 鄒族則有小米收穫祭典（homeyaya）與彰顯彪炳戰功的凱旋祭（mayasvi）；邵族有ulalaluan（祖靈籃）；賽夏族的「巴斯達隘矮靈祭」；布農族的「射耳祭」與小米祭；達悟族的「飛魚祭」；阿美族的豐收祭、太魯閣族的收穫祭與賽德克族的年祭等等祭典。",
      "ab": "Ida smparu bi qmita Utux Rudan ka seejiq tnpusu, snhiyi saw gaga mniq knglangan ka rdrudan, ida gaga qmlahang tnan, Tuxan ksun dha ka hiya. Duri ni seejiq tnpusu ga ida niqan nanaq knsmiyan dha, saw ka “homeyaya” ni “mayasvi” nChou, ulalaluan “nThau”, “Pastaay” nSaysyac, “malaqtainga” nBunun, “mivanoa” nTau, ilisin nAmis, Magay Bari nTruku ni “Smgasuc” nSeejiq dnii smiyan knlgan seejiq tnpusu Taywan.",
